Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:38.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介茫然！疼孩子之岩石之母！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着悲伤的妖气环绕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静 太安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有着悲伤的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.06,0:02:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有着悲伤的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有着悲伤的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把好不容易弄热的气愤弄暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才别打扰我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上是这里的人士请我来寻找妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每到夏天就跑出来偷食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在此振奋精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此探寻妖气…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风景真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 要吃饭请到此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是“佛灭”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭请到此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海滨店重建了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还是在赚重建金的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙有来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他虽然那个样子 可是也很会做生意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一只冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖弄色相是他的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在玩 你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须赚…赚…赚钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在今夏集够资金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就能开海滨冰果店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给我酬谢的打工钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲我过去有破坏约定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像你以前有遵守过约定咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介要买什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说 比基尼的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要今夏拼命的赚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天就能穿比基尼游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是父子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰 要不要冰棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买只冰棒好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 刚才不是买给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛 再买嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在偷窥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 我去救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何在那里走着呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 在寻找孩子之际…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真可怜 请让我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子能找到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重要的…孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩…子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是因为找孩子 那真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙有便当吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？太太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？太太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是龙之介的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 你忘了母亲了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事能开玩笑的说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会有这么漂亮的太太吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让你看证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲是适合和服的美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是跟老爸同伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都来愚弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事不能当玩笑说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 是你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的是要买比基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么弄不懂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快 愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快 愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是很饿了吧 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你也一起来此扒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意 这已是平常的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介去哪了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易 他母亲回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定害羞得不敢来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成为那变态老爸的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定地方有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那异样的吃相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是常人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许真的是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 地方人士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在这边吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找妖怪的事怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有食物被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必那么急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这妖怪可不是什么坏妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎环绕着一股感伤的乡愁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是渴望爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话听够了 快给我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他也会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先来喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久未见面的夫妇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是龙之介之母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错 是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会找到龙之介的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我妻子当妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话 这么美丽的太太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了这个也说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是尾巴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 这不是尾巴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子有必要求证了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的在找寻妖怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听他说 像那样集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为探查妖怪的气息的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来还真有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不平凡的气势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我的母亲在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会开玩笑的做此事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想确定此事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我必须要有尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那位伯母…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等等 拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子小龙认为那伯母是他母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那海吧 龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着那海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫喊着妈妈 向她怀中冲去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现妖怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想龙之介可能会拗脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会顺自己心意投向母亲怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是母亲怀中的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会更柔软的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来是妖怪之子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子 没有“这不是我妈”的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子 你怎么变这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大叔要玩到何时？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑！妖怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩石在跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你太太吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介 母亲是适合洋装的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子才是她要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:21:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚间出现诱拐达令的可疑之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受难于牡丹灯笼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:23:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是狐狸妖怪的迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑之光所引之地方是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪谈！卡啦喀隆女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:17.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连在梦中我都想追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:22.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在床底放了你的相片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:32.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明梦见自己轻飘飘的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:39.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在就要接吻时醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:48.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要紧紧抱住我喔 我一定会乖乖地等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:59.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人迫不及待 碍事的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:04.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着又觉得好难过 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的睡衣 请感受我赤裸裸的心情 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:23.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叹了一口气 彷佛要燃烧起来的蓝色星球之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.49,0:24:35.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要见了你 PESAMETEKIERO 在星空中踏步 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:46.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河的某处有你和我 MOBIUS的相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.60,0:24:57.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 痛苦时 PESAMERUTYO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.78,0:25:10.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是已约定好 PESAMERUTYO 即使等呆了 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:20.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论距离多远的星球 以MOBIUS之环相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.86,0:25:30.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 决定好了后 PESAMERUTYO

